# This folder doubles as the working dir (the app runs here and saves masters), so use
# default-DENY: git tracks ONLY the docs listed below. Everything else is ignored no matter
# what lands here — binaries, zips, saved masters (.mp3/.wav/.flac/.txt), demo audio, temp/,
# screenshots, videos. The binaries/zips ship via GitHub Releases, not the repo.
*

!.gitignore
!.gitattributes
!README.md
!HELP.md
!INSTALL.md
!LICENSE.txt
!THIRD-PARTY-LICENSES.txt
!wavmaster.jpg
